title: Top floor territorial view with Sunset-feel like a penthouse
posting_body: ['3924 243rd PL SE, #undisclosed, Bothell, WA 98021', 'Available 09/01/22!', 'Showing starts 08/04/22.', 'This top (3rd) floor, 2 bedroom corner condo offers territorial views overlooking Canyon Park Valley.', 'Enjoy gorgeous sunset every day.', 'Master bedroom with full bath and walk-in closet.', 'Garage, storage space as well as community pool, gym, hot tub, playground and clubhouse.', 'Easy access to I-405 and I-5 and close to major bus lines.', 'Sorry, no pets allowed.', 'Amenities', '• Territorial and Sunset Views', '• 1 garage and 1 assigned parking spot included', '• Hardwood', '• Carpet', '• Living Room', '• Breakfast Nook', '• Pantry', '• Full Master Bath', '• Storage Space/Room', '• Inside Laundry Room', '• Master Walk-in Closet', '• Remodeled', '• Fire Sprinklers', '• Double Pane Storm Windows', '• Community Pool', '• Community Workout Room', '• Community Clubhouse', '• HOA and garbage included', '• Award winning Northshore school district', 'Details', '• Beds/Baths: 2BD/2.0BA', '• Square Feet: 983', '• HOA, parking, garbage included in rent.', 'Tenant pays all other utilities.', 'Rental Terms', '• Rent: $2,250', "• Last month's rent: $2,250", '• Available: Showing starts 08/04/22, move in 09/01/22', '• Screening Fee: $40 per adult', '• Security Deposit: $1,500', '• HOA move in/move out fee: $400', '• 1 year lease', 'Email, text or call', 'show contact info', 'for showing.', 'Please provide details of your application - your financial qualification and number of renters, and etc.', 'before requesting a tour.', 'General Qualifications:', '-Gross income of at least 3 times the monthly rent', '-Good credit scores', '-Good rental and/or mortgage payment history - no late payments, bounced checks, or property damage', '-No evictions on record', '-No balances due to prior Landlords/Agents', '-No current accounts in collections', '**We do not accept comprehensive reusable tenant screening reports**']
